font-size:14.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;<br>mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;<br>mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:<br>0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;3、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:<br>宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;周报管理&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;周报管理是填报人员对项目每周的工作完成情况，对每个员工完成的工时数进行填报，然后申报给部门领导进行审核的过程。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.25pt;mso-list:l0&nbsp;level1&nbsp;lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;<br>mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;<br>mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:<br>0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;4、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:<br>宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;月报管理&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;月报管理是对每周填报的工时进行按月汇总，然后由生产部门的负责人进行申报，部门审核，再提交给其他部门进行审核的过程。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.25pt;mso-list:l0&nbsp;level1&nbsp;lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;<br>mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;<br>mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:<br>0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;5、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:<br>宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;工时汇总管理&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;工时汇总管理是针对生产部门自己承担的各个项目的所有填报工时的一个汇总，通过工时汇总管理，工时领导和各个生产部门可以清晰的看到自己部门的信息，并有效的核实填报工时信息的正确性。工时汇总管理包括所有部门工时费用、部门合同工时费用以及部门合同分月工时。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;margin-left:0cm;text-indent:24.25pt;mso-list:l0&nbsp;level1&nbsp;lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;<br>mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;<br>mso-bidi-font-family:宋体;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-font-kerning:<br>0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;6、&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight:normal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:<br>宋体;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;财务管理&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;font-family:楷体;mso-bidi-font-family:&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;;<br>mso-font-kerning:0pt;mso-bidi-language:EN-US&quot;&gt;财务管理主要是对项目当中的合同额、收款、成本情况进行统计，以进行绩效的测算和工资的统计。<br>主要功能有费用录入、收款登记、成本汇总、收入汇总等。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;/resource/image/qiyexinxihua/gongshiguanli4.png&quot;&gt;', '3', null, '2', '2015-07-06 15:23:21', '1');
