p;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:<br>Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;l&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font:7.0pt&nbsp;&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;产品功能简介&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br>mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:<br>Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;本系统通过路侧固定式信息采集设备，实时监测车况、路况信息，及时判别目标车辆的运行状态与风险级别，即时发布预警信息、管理对策与调度救援方案。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br>mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:<br>Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;智能预警系统功能图&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;<br>mso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0&nbsp;level1&nbsp;lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:<br>Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;l&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font:7.0pt&nbsp;&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;结构介绍&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br>mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:<br>Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;为了便于系统的结构设计与推广应用，系统采用模块化的设计结构，共划分为&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;6&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:<br>Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;个模块，分别为长下坡入口模块、区间测速模块、刹车鼓温度预警模块、隧道事件检测模块、断面车速监控模块、紧急避险车道监控救援指挥模块。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:<br>11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br>mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:<br>Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;（增加系统截图）&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:<br>11.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoListParagraph&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt;<br>mso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l0&nbsp;level1&nbsp;lfo1&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:Wingdings;mso-fareast-font-family:<br>Wingdings;mso-bidi-font-family:Wingdings&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-list:Ignore&quot;&gt;l&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font:7.0pt&nbsp;&amp;quot;Times&nbsp;New&nbsp;Roman&amp;quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;<br>mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;mso-fareast-font-family:宋体;mso-fareast-theme-font:<br>minor-fareast;mso-hansi-font-family:Calibri;mso-hansi-theme-font:minor-latin&quot;&gt;产品优势&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:14.0pt&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;<br>font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:Calibri;mso-ascii-theme-font:minor-latin;<br>ms