quot;&nbsp;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;new=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;总体结构&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;http://172.16.1.195:8087/resource/image/gongluyidongyujingxitong/yidongyujing1.jpg&quot;&nbsp;height=&quot;467&quot;&nbsp;width=&quot;409&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:<br>150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;&nbsp;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;new=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;数据获取设备&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25;<br>line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:<br>楷体&quot;&gt;数据获取设备包括交通流与路况检测子系统、气象与环境信息采集子系统、车辆定位定姿子系统、集中控制子系统、信息发布子系统、承载平台子系统六个子系统。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;&nbsp;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;new=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;分析决策软件平台&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:27.0pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25;<br>line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;line-height:150%;font-family:<br>楷体&quot;&gt;软件平台是以&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;GIS&lt;/span&gt;平台和车载数据库为支撑，由不同功能的软件模块构成，主要包括预警分析模块、预控决策模块、可视化模块、图表分析模块、人机交互模块和信息管理模块等六个软件模块。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;http://172.16.1.195:8087/resource/image/gongluyidongyujingxitong/image004.gif&quot;&gt;<br>&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:<br>12.0pt;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;br&nbsp;style=&quot;mso-ignore:vglayout&quot;&nbsp;clear=&quot;ALL&quot;&gt;<br><br>&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-family:宋体;mso-ascii-font-family:&quot;&nbsp;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;new=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;;=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;mso-hansi-font-family:&quot;times=&quot;&quot;&nbsp;roman&quot;&quot;=&quot;&quot;&gt;产品功能与工作流程：&lt;/span&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-indent:23.65pt;mso-char-indent-count:2.25;<br>line-height:150%&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;style=&quot;font-size:12.0pt;<br>line-height:150%;font-family:楷体&quot;&gt;本产品以车辆为前端数据采集平台，巡逻与停泊两种预警模式，实现公路运营信息监测、风险分析、预测、预警功能。&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;span&nbsp;lang=&quot;EN-US&quot;&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;<br><br>&lt;p&nbsp;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&nbsp;style=&quot;text-align:center;line-height:150%&quot;&nbsp;align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;img&nbsp;src=&quot;http://172.16.1.195:8087/resource/image/gongluyidongyujingxitong/image006